metadata.name: Aine
metadata.description:
Androgynous by Francisca Oyhanarte.
Francisca created 88 Androgynous with paper cut-outs and assembled them digitally. She used Pranic Healing techniques to energize them in order to bring positive and healing effects.
All the NFTs are 1/1s and come with a claimable 14"" x 14"" physical print.
If you are lucky when minting, you will get to collect one of the four animated Androgynous!

Verisart Certified: https://verisart.com/works/a741a37e-760a-4513-8864-d98a51947fd2
